thread.title: Royals rout Blue Jays 14-2, 1 win from World Series return

title: Royals rout Blue Jays 14-2, 1 win from World Series return
text:
> Sports Royals rout Blue Jays 14-2, 1 win from World Series return Kansas City Royals third baseman Mike Moustakas, left, and first baseman Eric Hosmer celebrate after defeating the Toronto Blue Jays 14-2 in Game 4 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, in Toronto. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
